{"tid":951742,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"仲有咩值得開心","createTime":"2018-12-22T14:50:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-22T18:30:14.000Z","uid":22480,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"c07c1358eeaea4ad11032d11b11a5b9edce7c935","tid":951742,"uid":22480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T14:50:05.000Z","msg":"番學頹<br />\n唔知入唔入到大學<br />\n<br />\n番工頹<br />\n知道自己打工根本唔會有錢<br />\n同啲有錢fd一齊番工已經知<br />\n佢為sip 時間我為生活<br />\n<br />\n見女朋友都頹<br />\n日日小事就唔開心要氹佢<br />\n<br />\n番屋企都頹<br />\n冇咩事都好少同老豆老母傾計<br />\n唔係我唔理佢 係佢要搵佢 佢先會同我講野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n諗住唔開心去做吓運動<br />\n打陣波又諗打咁耐都咁廢 跑個步就會一路諗遺憾<br />\n<br />\n以前既興趣今日已經冇掂<br />\n成屋樂器 但係已經冇心情掂佢<br />\n<br />\n好似做咩都唔會開心 已經好耐冇由心底笑過<br />\n好辛苦 有冇人明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2027ade02ca553f0472e8508a81bc7c14f2c87a1","tid":951742,"uid":107364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T14:57:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"579bd631f5bb9cc4aeaf3e18b85f74e7231afe2b","tid":951742,"uid":22480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2027ade02ca553f0472e8508a81bc7c14f2c87a1","tid":951742,"uid":107364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T14:57:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T14:59:44.000Z","msg":"慢慢變心理負擔了"},{"pid":"d2a2f3c207ff4b14df809c1ee9e535add2fcce78","tid":951742,"uid":107364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T15:00:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c5c157247bf60142b1882131692bb2045f8c2c53","tid":951742,"uid":22480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d2a2f3c207ff4b14df809c1ee9e535add2fcce78","tid":951742,"uid":107364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"579bd631f5bb9cc4aeaf3e18b85f74e7231afe2b","tid":951742,"uid":22480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2027ade02ca553f0472e8508a81bc7c14f2c87a1","tid":951742,"uid":107364,"like":0,"dislike"